node.text:
See the new train station we are design for old town city center of Jiaxing, a city in zhejiang province, China. 

1. Turn the ground level to a huge park.
2. Restoration of more than 100 yrs old train station. 
3. Build new one ard it.
4. Put all function and traffic underground, free the land. 
5. Insert commercial spaces to make old town more lively with possibilities for future development

Now project under construction will be completed in July 2021!

#madprojects #madcity #jiaxingtrainstation #givethiscityapark #parkgreen #returnlandtopeople #oldtrainstationnewdesign #historytofuture #travelthroughtime

node.title: Mad releases jiaxing train station design

node.text:
Set between the young vibrant city of Shenzhen, and the quiet oceanfront, “Shenzhen Bay Culture Park” juxtaposes two transcendental scales of time – the ‘ancient’ and the ‘future’ – through the setting of an ethereal artistic urban landscape. 
Animation by SAN ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ @mayansong_mad

node.text: Tokyo Olympics Ends. Eyes are now looking at the 2024 Paris Olympics. In 2020, MAD released design proposal for 2024 Paris Olympics’ Aquatic Center - “The Power of Water”. The proposal envisioned the sports facility as an urban public artwork showcases the beauty and hope of Paris. The energetic curves of the translucent building change with the sunlight and the sky. Natural light is able to enter the interior, creating a continuous play of light and shadow. #madarchitects #mayansong #aquacenter #olympics #olympics2024

Six years ago, 2015, before the Harbin Opera House was put to use, MAD collaborated with @shenweidancearts for a short film showing the sparkle between art and architecture. It’s still sparkling after all these years.

node.text:
MAD unveils the design for the Aranya “cloud center” in Qinhuangdao, China. The building is designed to appear as a “floating cloud by the sea”. Its perceived “cloud” form is made possible through a series of monumental structural overhangs, with largest reaching 30 meters in length. Upon completion, the scheme will offer a new multipurpose public space for Aranya, including a press conference room, small theater and exhibition space.
#madarchitects #mayansong #aranya #cloud
